      1047,
      1242,
      1117
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\textbf{B.} \\ |\\overrightarrow{AA_1} + \\overrightarrow{C_1D} + \\overrightarrow{C_1D_1}| = 0.\n$$"
